---
title: Coconut and Sweet Potato Curry with baby corn and jasmine rice
description: This slightly spicy Thai-inspired curry boasts an array of vibrant veg. Tender baby corn, softened roasted sweet potato and piquant chilli all bring a different element to the table. Served on a bed of zesty lime rice and topped with coriander, this dish is fresh as well as filling.
